ol.li: Each process gets equal time slice (e.g., 100ms)
On expiry, current moved to queue tail
Head of queue becomes new RUNNING
New processes added to queue tail Time Complexity: O(1) for all operations

div.p: add_to_queue(proc) proc.next = NULL if tail == NULL: head = tail = proc proc.prev = NULL else: tail.next = proc proc.prev = tail tail = proc
pick_next() if head == NULL: return current next = head head = head.next if head == NULL: tail = NULL else: head.prev = NULL next.state = RUNNING return next
